latestPosts.caption:
Udaivilas & Trident—two architectural marvels, each carrying a soul of its own. One, a masterpiece of grandeur, where golden domes kiss the morning light and endless corridors whisper tales of royalty. The other, a haven of understated elegance, where serene courtyards and tranquil waters invite you to slow down and just be.

10 days, eight events, and a dreamlike experience that now comes to an end. But some endings aren’t farewells—they’re echoes of moments that stay with you.

This time, holding the camera, I didn’t just capture beauty—I lived it.

ज़िंदगी कितनी ख़ूबसूरत है, ये बस सोच का खेल है—हर एहसास नया, हर कहानी अनसुनी, पर ये किरदार… पुराना है।

.
#lovemylife #lifeisbeautiful

latestPosts.caption:
"Om Lakshminarayanaya Namah"

This tattoo is a part of my spiritual journey. The concept came to me when I had a vision of Lord Lakshmi-Narayan in a dream. At that moment, I realized their arrival was destined in my life. My artist friend played a huge role in bringing this unique design to life. After 14+12  hours of hard work, the divine form of Lakshminarayan was created on my hand. This tattoo isn't just a design; it’s a manifestation of my connection with my divine Lord, and it gives me strength and self-confidence every day.
Thank you so much: @madabouttattoo_ @jayant_madabouttattoo

#lovemylife #lifeisbeautiful

latestPosts.caption:
DDLJ Diwali2024 By @jaipur_hopshop 
For this event, Raghvendra @lowercase.guyy shared his vision and said, Guys! we need to create something grand this Diwali. I want to host an event in Jaipur for its people, celebrating Diwali in a completely traditional way, bringing everyone together like never before. But everything must be aesthetic and on point—just like a Bollywood movie. It should feel as magical as Kajol and Shah Rukh’s Diwali in DDLJ/K3G
.
.
